    {
        "content": "<p>Note that <code>#check Nat.iterate_ind (α := fun i ↦ α (i + 37)) f</code> typecheks, so Lean has no real way of guessing <code>α</code> from <code>f</code>, and in your example is guessing a different one.</p>",
