    {
        "content": "<p>In your original example there is also the problem that <code>Nat.iterate_ind</code> is defined for an <code>α</code> taking values in <code>Type</code> and you apply with <code>α</code> taking value in any <code>Sort</code>. If you fix it using <code>Sort*</code> everywhere then <code>rfl</code> proves the theorem.</p>",
